precision is mechanical once the external compiler is upgraded.

**Conventions** (HZBS 2007):
  - σ₁ = diag(R₁, Rτ) with R₁ = e^(-i4π/5), Rτ = e^(i3π/5).
  - σ₂ = F · σ₁ · F (Bonesteel-Hormozi-Simon F-matrix).
  - T_NC[1,1] = e^(iπ/4) = ζ₈ = ζ₄₀⁵ ∈ Q(ζ₄₀).
  - Distance: spectral (operator) norm after global-phase removal.

